data.description: Perfect Family Vaulted Ceiling, 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage Home located in a quiet area.  Newer wood-look tiles throughout the kitchen, dining area, Master Bedroom, and large living room. Plenty of room at the kitchen island for barstool seating and gathering. The dining area off of the Kitchen provides enough room for a true family dining table with a view through a large window.    Enjoy your Screened-covered Lanai accessed from the Dining Area & living room with wall-to-wall Patio Sliders.  The master bedroom is split from the guest rooms with its own spacious private master bathroom including walking-in closets, decorative tiled shower, dual sinks, and a water closet.  The guest bathroom is situated between both guest rooms.  Enjoy the large backyard with a concrete patio and plenty of room for a pool! New roof in process.  Buyers add your TLC and enjoy SW Florida living.
